The service has created a "Data Bank of executive proceedings" for the convenience of citizens.
This special electronic application is available not only on the regional websites of the Federal Service for Social Security and Security, but also on social networks and mobile communication devices iPad, iPhone and smartphone.
The data bank contains information on the enforcement proceedings initiated by the Kalmykia prosecutors against all debtors, - explains assistant to the head of the Federal Trade Commission of Russia in Kazakhstan Delgir Bodgaeva.
"When debts exist, the system displays information on the number and date of the execution; the name of the body that issued the executive sheet or other act; its number, amount and type of debt; the address of the court bailiff department; the name of the court bailiff-executor; contact telephone.
